topPRs.title: Integrate Moondream into Twitter and Discord
topPRs.author: vladkashka56
topPRs.body:
Get the description of an image uploaded to Discord or Twitter and add it to the context so Ruby can "see" the image.
The description of the image is added to the recentMessages state variable.
